                        <condition key="deficient">The front board is missing; one fol. and half
                           covered by a textile have the function to replace it.
 The original
                           sewing is for the most part missing. The Ms. has been resewn with recent
                           threads.
 A few folios are misplaced (e.g., fol. 9), some are
                           possibly missing (e.g., between <locus target="#8v">8v</locus> and <locus target="#10r">10r</locus>).
 Several fols. are damaged at the
                           edges; <locus target="#1r">1r</locus> is for the most part destroyed, a
                           part of the text is lost.
 Many fols. are affected by
                           humidity.</condition>
